        <title>基于麒麟系统kylin_v10的Qt程序权限问题笔记</title>
        <link>https://ynhugo.github.io/p/%E5%9F%BA%E4%BA%8E%E9%BA%92%E9%BA%9F%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9Fkylin_v10%E7%9A%84qt%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E6%9D%83%E9%99%90%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</link>
